\" /> 我讀緊個間 既actuarial science 全英第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  由以前英文 dse 得個3 到依家 IELTS 6.5 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲係大學識到好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利：dse 中文u 通識 1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCity<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b160dad42e150c29e7f8026cab466bc8471d39c6","tid":501464,"uid":144982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:30:07.000Z","msg":"下面啲人咪撚再理鳩佢 條友唔知吾撚夠未"},{"pid":"1beb0d0150453ade9d22b90c8bf9698b2ee531e1","tid":501464,"uid":20213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:31:34.000Z","msg":"浸鹼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死撚左未呀<br />\n連登真係垃圾 咁堅持用吾都有一堆人覆<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b574172fc28da860740e3cbbcb2221e5471dbc82","tid":501464,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:49:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自問讀書吾叻,由中三開始英文味合格個既個既我,究竟要付出幾多努力先可以入到全球top100既大學.人地個個band 1仔讀2年 community college就入勁u,而我...cc前要讀多年language school,入到community college要付出好多好多既努力仲要讀多年先入到問ok既u.諗住入到u可以開開心心讀自己想讀既major,點知...炒撚左final C撚埋,逼住要轉major.個感覺係自己付出左好多努力都得吾到想要既成果.我知自己吾係讀書材料,吾似其他人會諗咩first hon, master degree,但求2.0畢業我好滿足.我好比心機睇reading,點知查字典既時間多個我睇.我比好多心機寫essay,點知grammar廢不在話下,連thesis同topic sentences既connection都做得吾好.有時好予盾,好想叫fd幫我睇文,又驚自己倚賴左個fd,又驚自己煩到人.<br />\n<br />\n其實對於dse拎12分既band 3仔黎講,係外國讀大學真係1件好痛苦既事.講錢,我吾係咩有錢仔,只係死好命有張綠卡.講親情,我同父母關係好差.同呀爸好小接觸,同呀媽傾次次都嘈.講朋友,自問對每個真係每個當朋友既都拎個心出黎,不過好多人都吾想理我.或者...我太煩膠,淨係識chur住人😪次次溝女都吾成功,<a href=\"http://仲嚇親個女仔.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BB%B2%E5%9A%87%E8%A6%AA%E5%80%8B%E5%A5%B3%E4%BB%94.cc&d=l5NSWSY8HZggNMti%2Ba%2FOoDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=818e7d6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">仲嚇親個女仔.cc</a>既social life好差,第1年仲比個host蝦😭😭到而家入左u先好返小小,算係有幾個朋友<br />\n<br />\n好多人話去外國好好,揸靚車,食鬼妹,返到香港又叫浸個下鹼水<br />\n<br />\n有d人又話,其實好多人背後付出左好多努力只係你吾知.<br />\n<br />\n可能你地全部都岩,不過我想講你吾係我,你吾會明我呢種感覺...</blockquote><br />\n巴打同我好似 只係我成績冇你咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fac2b34cdba673c158357dbc6bd020c80b30754","tid":501464,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Dse 13 分 出國2年後讀到 actuarial science <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我讀緊個間 既actuarial science 全英第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  由以前英文 dse 得個3 到依家 IELTS 6.5 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲係大學識到好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利：dse 中文u 通識 1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n6.5都拎出黎講 只不過係外國入學最低要求 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我黎左3年ielts先拎到6,之前考左5次都係5或者5.5</blockquote><br />\n考5次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 錢多</blockquote><br />\n屌有錢真係好，我冇錢入唔到八大只可以係香港讀啲濕鳩學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class